<P>
   Sports stories in sight at this hour from The New York Times
News Service for use in papers of Sunday, Nov. 28:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BKN-ARATON-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports column on Doc Rivers, the
