   LIPSYTE-COLUMN (Undated) _ Robert Lipsyte assesses the
forthcoming book, ``Taboo: Why Black Athletes Dominate Sports and
Why We're Afraid to Talk About It,'' by the documentary producer
Jon Entine, a book that grew out of the 1989 documentary by Tom
Brokaw.
