   TALKSHOW-PRIEST (Miami) _ Prayer is standard before every taping
of ``Padre Alberto,'' a talk show on the Telemundo Spanish-language
network that delves into domestic violence, incest, sex addiction
and other issues common to daytime programming but that unlike
other shows has a Roman Catholic priest as its host. By Mireya
Navarro.
