<HEADLINE>
RABBIS MADE THEIR MARK ON TEXAS HISTORY
</HEADLINE>
 (Art available) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TARA DOOLEY 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
