kids how to resist smoking, alcohol and drugs. Cynics might scoff.
But not Arizona State University. ASU's Hispanic Research Center is
state coordinator for the tobacco money and is seeking applications
from school districts, much to the dismay of anti-smoking
advocates. Story will move in the ``A'' category. &QL;
